Forget sequins or glitter, Anya Hindmarch used Daz, Ariel and even digestive biscuits as handbag embellishment at her AW14 show today.

The British accessories designer transformed her London Fashion Week catwalk-turned-conveyor-belt into supermarket sweep with dancing salesmen, glamorous lady shoppers pushing trollies and all the usual household essentials transformed into handbags.

Anya unveiled her crisp packet clutch last season but has taken her design skills a step further.

